{
  "stem": "21731.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They flew from Italy, I think, to Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had the base in Italy somewhere.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Italy was already freed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, we didn't know about that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the Moroccans marched in-- black people, the first black people I saw in my life.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never saw a black person.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were free.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We could do what we wanted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The German were our prisoners now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I think we did the best of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- the Moroccans got at once into this Gasthof.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were a lot of Gasthof.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They throw the Germans out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I got a bigger room because I was not German.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was a Pole.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They made their canteen in this Gasthof, you know, for all the officers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And a funny thing happened, that the officer in charge of this canteen fell in love with me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I didn't know what to do because he really-- he gave me whatever I wanted.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, I, I wanted only food, so Jan could have-- Jan was happy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I kept Jan very near me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Not that I was afraid that he will do something to me, but it was a bit unpleasant.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was very elegant, very good-looking, black, black like--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you could speak French with him because he was Moroccan--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--or--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] --a little bit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But anyway, he wanted to marry me and said that when, when I marry him, I will get very fat because they-- all women in Morocco have to be fat.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I will have all teeth out and will get all gold teeth because that's what they did.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All, all these officers had all gold teeth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The German made a fortune out of it because they had the-- had the gold from the Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they had to give it to the Moroccans.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
